This notice describes the intended per-directory licensing. If an
individual source file lacks an SPDX-License-Identifier header, or if
the header is inconsistent with this notice, the conflict shall be
resolved in favor of the source-file header when present, and in favor
of this notice when the source-file header is absent. When both are
absent, the file is unlicensed and may not be used, copied, modified,
or distributed.
